{"title":"Upbound UXP AWS Provider & API Calls","description":"## Upbound UXP AWS Provider & API Calls\n\nComplements the UXP Overview, Min Set and MR TTR dashboards by surfacing metrics that those examples omit, with an emphasis on **AWS Cloud SDK API calls** made by the Upbound AWS providers and on the Crossplane composition pipeline.\n\nMetric sources (scraped at `:8080/metrics` and exposed under the Datadog `uxp.` namespace):\n\n- **AWS Cloud SDK API calls** – `upjet_resource_ext_api_duration` (bucket/count/sum), labelled by `operation` (connect, observe, create, update, delete). Measures how long each Cloud SDK call to AWS takes.\n- **Managed resource fleet** – `crossplane_managed_resource_exists` / `_ready` / `_synced` by `gvk`.\n- **Reconciliation** – `controller_runtime_reconcile_total` (by result), `controller_runtime_reconcile_time_seconds`, `controller_runtime_active_workers`, `controller_runtime_reconcile_timeouts_total`, `workqueue_retries_total`, `workqueue_longest_running_processor_seconds`.\n- **Kubernetes API client** – `rest_client_requests_total` by `code` and `method`, `leader_election_master_status`.\n- **Composition functions** (Crossplane core) – `function_run_function_seconds`, `function_run_function_request_total`, request/response payload bytes, gRPC code & result severity.\n- **XR engine** (Crossplane core) – `circuit_breaker_events_total` / `_opens_total` / `_closes_total`, `engine_controllers_started_total`, `engine_watches_started_total`.\n- **Webhooks & certificates** – `controller_runtime_webhook_requests_total` (by `code` and `webhook`), `controller_runtime_webhook_requests_in_flight`, `controller_runtime_webhook_panics_total`, `controller_runtime_conversion_webhook_panics_total`, `certwatcher_read_certificate_total` / `_errors_total`.\n- **Runtime health & saturation** – `controller_runtime_reconcile_panics_total`, `controller_runtime_terminal_reconcile_errors_total`, `workqueue_queue_duration_seconds` (queue wait), `controller_runtime_max_concurrent_reconciles`, `process_network_receive_bytes_total` / `_transmit_bytes_total`, `go_sync_mutex_wait_total_seconds_total`, `go_gc_duration_seconds`, `go_threads`, `process_virtual_memory_bytes`, and open/max file-descriptor utilization.","widgets":[{"id":1000000000007777,"definition":{"type":"image","url":"https://static.upbound.io/marketing/upbound_uxp_logo.svg","sizing":"cover","has_background":true,"has_border":true,"vertical_align":"center","horizontal_align":"center"},"layout":{"x":0,"y":0,"width":2,"height":2}},{"id":1000000000015554,"definition":{"title":"AWS Cloud SDK API Call Rate by Operation","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","show_legend":true,"legend_layout":"auto","legend_columns":["avg","min","max","value","sum"],"type":"timeseries","requests":[{"formulas":[{"formula":"query1"}],"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:upjet_resource_ext_api_duration.count{*} by {operation,pod}.as_rate()"}],"response_format":"timeseries","style":{"palette":"dog_classic","line_type":"solid","line_width":"normal"},"display_type":"line"}]},"layout":{"x":2,"y":0,"width":4,"height":2}},{"id":1000000000023331,"definition":{"title":"AWS Cloud SDK API Call Errors (connect/observe/create/update/delete)","title_size":"16","title_align":"left","show_legend":true,"legend_layout":"auto","legend_columns":["avg","min","max","value","sum"],"type":"timeseries","requests":[{"formulas":[{"formula":"query1"}],"queries":[{"name":"query1","data_source":"metrics","query":"sum:upjet_resource_ext_api_duration.count{*} by {operation,kind}.as_count()"}],"response_format":"timeseries","style":{"palette":"dog_classic","line_type":"solid","line_width":"normal"},"display_type":"line"}]},"layout":{"x":6,"y":0,"width":4,"height":2}},{"id":1000000000031108,"definition":{"type":"note","content":"AWS Cloud SDK API Calls — external provider→AWS request latency & throughput (upjet_resource_ext_api_duration)","background_color":"blue","font_size":"18","text_alig